1) Download the file and unzip it (or copy the code into a lua capable editor)
2) Start the Myo Connect app on your computer.
3) On Mac (not sure for windows) click on the toolbar icon for the Myo connect app and scroll down to "Myo Scripts Manager."
4) Click "+ Add Script"
5) Navigate to the location of the unzipped file
6) Open Spotify
7) Shake and bake


Gestures Currently Supported (and the respective commands):

Fingers Spread :: Play/Pause
Swipe Left :: Previous Track
Swipe Right :: Next Track

Fist(hold):
    Roll RIGHT :: Volume Up
    Roll LEFT :: Volume Down
